{"tid":542383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老闆有精神分裂","createTime":"2018-01-27T12:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T13:05:37.000Z","uid":49290,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1edaaf9491f0475d011eb8029db5ef4ddaad15c3","tid":542383,"uid":49290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"入左間公司做無耐發現老細有兩個人格其中一個叫Ivan Chan 另外一個叫Edmond Wong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我公司有個獨立廁所淨係老闆同佢老婆先會去 其他員工就去樓層個廁所 本身以為佢係唔想比人知佢係老闆先有兩個名 但係後尾發現佢叫Ivan Chan個陣會用個獨立廁所 叫Edmond Wong個陣就會出去用樓層個廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且佢老婆都會叫佢Edmond或者Ivan 佢叫Edmond個陣個人暴躁好多 叫Ivan個陣就好串嘴 有一次佢聽電話 個陣佢係Ivan 但係人地話搵Edmond 佢話等等 然後就切換個人格 好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1437a20bf552613ba70d4a04a6849002170c2b","tid":542383,"uid":165890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"其實男人都係。屌前另一個人，射後都另一個人。"},{"pid":"8dcc5aed0d07dbbd8814ea6354def3bdaf27e0c6","tid":542383,"uid":49290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"唔知佢會唔會知另外一個人格做過d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢老婆就好可以有兩個老公"},{"pid":"1861129573b5aed08e4853a61dfc3c2a840e2891","tid":542383,"uid":138462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"個啲叫人格分裂 唔係精神分裂"},{"pid":"24623e1a588d03fb5a0024fe35e728d422f4d090","tid":542383,"uid":138462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"人格分裂要處理喎 同佢老婆講啦"},{"pid":"4f881d7b4fd0c45a801cb9b210d84cfe94ad7d35","tid":542383,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea4b39e5f1465baddec128e1c1822b59895946d9","tid":542383,"uid":49290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24623e1a588d03fb5a0024fe35e728d422f4d090","tid":542383,"uid":138462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s